<h3><a href="https://github.wpilib.org/allwpilib/docs/release/java/edu/wpi/first/wpilibj2/command/CommandScheduler.html#setActiveButtonLoop(edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.event.EventLoop)" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">CommandScheduler (WPILib API 2024.3.2)</a></h3>

