    <h4>
      <a href="https://github.com/wpilibsuite/allwpilib/issues/5903" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Periodically calling CommandXboxController button functions causes CommandScheduler loop overruns</a>
    </h4>

    <div class="github-info">
      <div class="date">
        opened <span class="discourse-local-date" data-format="ll" data-date="2023-11-10" data-time="04:47:10" data-timezone="UTC">04:47AM - 10 Nov 23 UTC</span>
      </div>


